h.kg/1473019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1473019</a><br />\n<br />\n眾所鳩知，港豬剩係關心飲飲食食同身體健康<br />\n<br />\n咁點樣可撼動到佢哋有恐慌而同我哋企同一陣線呢？<br />\n<br />\n就係所有人搭地鐵都帶豬咀！！！而且身上貼定張文宣解釋「我唔係示威者，但長期吸入地鐵嘅催淚氣體會死」，<br />\n<br />\n日日帶，天天帶，只要夠多人戴就可以帶起嗰心理恐慌，保證畀起不合作塞鐵更加撼動港豬<br />\n<br />\nWtsapp/Facebook文宣上線喇<br />\n<br />\n【手動轉】<br />\n<br />\n警方已在不同的地鐵站內或附近發射催淚彈，而催淚粉末會黏附在地鐵的電梯扶手、售票機甚至通風系統及冷氣系統。<br />\n<br />\n而港鐵目前未有適當的過濾措施，站內空氣將受嚴重污染，而催淚煙物質會化成為劇毒物質山埃，更會殘留達一年。呼籲各位乘客乘搭港鐵時，佩帶豬咀口罩，以保障自身的健康。"},{"pid":"dd3e9e1c81de2edef90b4a8702aa0b55d20542a1","tid":1473172,"uid":264771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:27:35.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"0fa37d30ccf4a5b7810be30e53d90b3215d5c8fa","tid":1473172,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:28:32.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"a7d9d144cffd3aca9a3ce183ea6365bc8979c74c","tid":1473172,"uid":199902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8d753a5f6fb1ff2b3d1fbf5b40c053198e350a2a","tid":1473172,"uid":277589,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:41:00.000Z","msg":"工農兵商人人平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:30:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Yx5RePFjunw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYx5RePFjunw&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=adb1d1a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Yx5RePFjunw</a>"},{"pid":"1025d98e47f9cdf40b5f26d88088426dd0b0395e","tid":1473172,"uid":156582,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"7b5fc021336f37a7a3b8fa466e2ae1673f187ad1","tid":1473172,"uid":203393,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:57:27.000Z","msg":"改國旗好似犯法嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:30:36.000Z","msg":"改越南國旗都犯法?"},{"pid":"7e8371d60cf52a459746eb9eb037debdae7814c0","tid":1473172,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike"